(42, 1, 2, 58, 2, 3, 3, 'eyewitnesses, and ministers of the word', 'Connection of Eyewitnesses and Salvation', 'Both passages emphasize the role of eyewitnesses in conveying the message of salvation. Luke mentions ''eyewitnesses'' who delivered the word, while Hebrews refers to those who ''heard him'' confirming the message.', 'theme', 0.37, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
