(42, 9, 11, 23, 61, 1, 1, 'healed them that had need of healing', 'Healing and Proclamation Connection', 'Both passages emphasize healing and proclaiming good news. Luke speaks of Jesus healing those in need, while Isaiah describes an anointed figure bringing good tidings and binding up the brokenhearted.', 'theme', 0.314, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
