(42, 13, 28, 40, 22, 13, 13, 'there shall be weeping and gnashing of teeth', 'Weeping and Gnashing of Teeth', 'Both passages emphasize the theme of weeping and gnashing of teeth as a consequence of exclusion from the kingdom of God. They depict a stark contrast between those accepted into the kingdom and those cast out into darkness.', 'theme', 0.32799999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
