(42, 13, 28, 19, 112, 10, 10, 'gnashing of teeth', 'Weeping and Gnashing of Teeth', 'This connection highlights the theme of grief and despair experienced by the wicked. Both passages emphasize ''gnashing of teeth'' as a response to being excluded from the blessings of God''s kingdom.', 'theme', 0.314, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
