(42, 20, 22, 16, 5, 4, 4, 'tribute', 'Tribute and Authority Connection', 'This connection highlights the theme of tribute and obligation to authority. Both passages address the concept of paying tribute, whether to Caesar or for the king''s tribute.', 'theme', 0.314, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
